query:
INSERT INTO "table" (warehouse_id,
                             table_id,
                             table_format_version,
                             last_column_id,
                             last_sequence_number,
                             last_updated_ms,
                             last_partition_id
                             )
        (
            SELECT $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
            WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1
                FROM active_tables
                WHERE active_tables.warehouse_id = $1
                    AND active_tables.table_id = $2))
        RETURNING "table_id"
